```
❌ node_modules/      ❌ 說明文件/         ❌ .git/
❌ projects/          ❌ python-main/      ❌ src/
❌ dist/              ❌ build/            ❌ assets/
❌ components/        ❌ modules/          ❌ utils/
❌ config/            ❌ lib/              ❌ scripts/
❌ docs/              ❌ examples/         ❌ tests/
