### 檔案黑名單
```
❌ README.md          ❌ CHANGELOG.md      ❌ CONTRIBUTING.md
❌ LICENSE.md         ❌ INSTALL.md        ❌ USAGE.md
❌ API.md             ❌ DEPLOY.md         ❌ CONFIG.md
